articles.title: Julianna R. Calabrese
articles.description: This website is a big work-in-progress - excuse the mess!
articles.contents: I am a graduate student in the Clinical Psychology Program at The Ohio State University. My research interests include emotion dysregulation, facial affective behavior, and quantitative methods. I received my Bachelor’s degree in Psychology at Smith College under Dr. Nnamdi Pole, Dr. Randi Garcia, and Dr. Randy Frost.
